 Galvatron watched as the lizard grabbed her. "Oh hell no." He flew off after 
the lizard bot. He was much quicker with his advanced tecehnology and flew 
over him and stopped infront about 5 feet. He sent a power surge from his 
chest and a fire from both his hands. Trying hard not to hit the bot. God 
neptune crept behind the lizard attacking Dark Mouse and send  a  Grenade 
behind his back and it was set to explode about 5 inches from his back.
